  <brief_title>Combined Afib Ablation and RA Denervation for the Maintenance of Sinus Rhythm and Management of Resistant Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Combined Atrial Fibrillation Ablation and Renal Artery Denervation for the Maintenance of Sinus Rhythm and Management of Resistant Hypertension</official_title>
